---
title: Cornflake and Honey-Crusted Chicken with Parmesan Broccoli and Yellow Rice with Peas
description: We’re using cornflakes for a crispy-crunchy coating on juicy chicken breasts. A hint of honey, paprika, and garlic perfects the sweet and salty flavour combo. Psst - we’ve also added a bit of heart-healthy turmeric spice to the rice to give it that gorgeous yellow hue!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/corn-flake-and-honey-crusted-chicken-f82accb3.jpg
